Class SimpleEntryView<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hazelcast.map.impl.SimpleEntryView<K,V>
  • Type Parameters:
    K - the type of key.
    V - the type of value.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    EntryView<K,V>, DataSerializable, IdentifiedDataSerializable, Versioned

    public class SimpleEntryView<K,V>
extends Object
implements EntryView<K,V>, IdentifiedDataSerializable, Versioned
    SimpleEntryView is an implementation of EntryView and also it is writable.
